Usage: report_mode [-help] <instance_list> [-view <view_name>]
                   [> <filename[.gz]>] [>> <filename[.gz]>]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<instance_list>     # List of instances (string, required)
-view <view_name>   # Specifies analysis view (string, optional)
> <filename[.gz]>   # Redirects output to the specified file
                    # (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <filename[.gz]>  # Redirects output to the specified file
                    # (redirect_operator, optional)